N
N=\sum_{k=0}^n a_k\cdot10^k 
N
11\mid N \Longleftrightarrow 11\mid \sum_{k=0}^n(-1)^k  a_k 
\begin{eqnarray} N = f(10) &&= a_n 10^n +\,\cdots+a_1 10 + a_0 \\ {\rm where}\ \ f(x) &&= a_n\, x^n\,+\,\cdots\,+a_1\, x\, + a_0\end{eqnarray}
\ {\rm mod}\ 11\!:\,\ \color{#c00}{10\equiv -1}\,\Rightarrow\, f(\color{#c00}{10})\equiv f(\color{#c00}{-1})\,
\ 11\mid N=f(10)\iff 11\mid f(-1),\,
